## Architecture Overview

```
┌────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ TOKOVO ARCHITECTURE │
├──────────┬───────────┬───────────┬──────────┬───────────┬─────────────┤
│ DSL │ IR │ Compiler │ Engine │ Layout │ Renderer │
│ (Author) │ (Schema) │ (Lowering)│ (Runtime)│ (Position)│ (Render) │
└──────────┴───────────┴───────────┴──────────┴───────────┴─────────────┘
↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓
"receive()" TrackEvent RuntimeEvent State Positions Pixels
```

### How Your Plugin Fits In

```
┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│ YOUR PLUGIN │
├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│ dsl/ → DSL helpers (TrackBuilder) │
│ ir/ → Event schemas (payloads.ts) │
│ lowering/ → IR → RuntimeEvent translation │
│ runtime/ → Reducer (event → state) │
│ layout/ → State → positions computation │
│ views/ → Positions → React components │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

