## UI Strategy Pattern

### The Pattern

```typescript
// Define interface
interface UIStrategy {
Header: React.FC<HeaderProps>;
    MessageBubble: React.FC<MessageBubbleProps>;
        InputArea: React.FC<InputAreaProps>;
            tokens: UIThemeTokens;
            }

            // iOS implementation
            const IOSStrategy: UIStrategy = {
            Header: IOSHeader,
            MessageBubble: IOSMessageBubble,
            ...
            };

            // Android implementation
            const AndroidStrategy: UIStrategy = {
            Header: AndroidHeader,
            MessageBubble: AndroidMessageBubble,
            ...
            };

            // Usage in screen
            const strategy = UIStrategyRegistry.forPlatform("ios");
            <strategy.Header conversation={conv} />
            ```

            ### Adding a Custom Theme (e.g., Ghibli)

            1. Create `views/themes/ghibli/strategy.tsx`
            2. Implement UIStrategy interface
            3. Register with `UIStrategyRegistry.register(GhibliStrategy)`
            4. Use: `UIStrategyRegistry.get("{{ kebabCase name }}-ghibli")`

